title: Avengers - The Private War of Dr. Doom (1963, Bchry-DCP)
description: Avengers - The Private War of Dr. Doom (1963, Bchry-DCP), hardcover edition. Collects Avengers 150-156, Annual 6; Super-Villain Team-Up 9. Doctor Doom is being a dick...again. Only this time, Attuma (from Atlantis) wants to stop his plans so HE can be a bigger dick. The Avengers get caught up in this dick-swinging contest. Thanks to Bchry-DCP for the scans, please seed and enjoy.
